Package com.schibsted.android.sdk

Interface Summary
SPiDAuthorizationListener Listener interface for a SPiD authorization request.
SPiDRequestListener Listener interface for a SPiD request.
 

Class Summary
SPiDAccessToken Contains a access token response from SPiD
SPiDAuthorizationRequest Contains methods for authorization to SPiD, it handles both WebView and browser redirect.
SPiDClient Created with IntelliJ IDEA.
SPiDConfiguration Contains a configuration for the SPiD SDK
SPiDConfigurationBuilder Builder class for SPiDConfiguration
SPiDKeychain Helper class used to securely encrypt/decrypt access token to SharedPreferences
SPiDLogger Helper class used for debug logging
SPiDRequest Contains a request to SPiD, note that each request can only be used once since it extends AsyncTask
SPiDResponse Contains a response from SPiD
SPiDTokenRequest Contains a access token request to SPiD
SPiDUtils Util class used for generating device fingerprint
SPiDWebViewClient SPiD implementation of WebViewClient, it should be subclassed if a custom WebViewClient is needed
